data.description: Want country living while still being in town? Then come take a look at this updated home surrounded by beautiful oak trees on amost 3 acres. The home features the original wood floors throughout with an amazing, updated kitchen complete with soft touch cabinets and drawers along with granite counters, a double stainless sink, and 5 burner gas range stove. Bathroom features a tumbled stone bathtub/shower with granite counter tops. This home is a must-see!
